    <h2 data-i18n-en="Does the method work? Three questions."
        data-i18n-zh="方法有效吗？三个问题。">Does the method work? Three questions.</h2>

    <!-- ── Q1: Does more data help? ── -->
    <h3 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; color: var(--accent-cyan);"
      data-i18n-en="Question 1: Does collecting more snapshots improve accuracy?"
      data-i18n-zh="问题 1：收集更多快照能提高精度吗？">Question 1: Does collecting more snapshots improve accuracy?</h3>

    <p data-i18n-en="Yes. The error has two independent parts — a statistical part that shrinks with more data, and a discretization floor set by how far apart the snapshots are."
       data-i18n-zh="是的。误差有两个独立部分——随着更多数据缩小的统计部分，以及由快照间隔决定的离散化下限。">
      Yes. The error has two independent parts — a statistical part that shrinks with more data, and a discretization floor set by how far apart the snapshots are.
    </p>

    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin: 1rem 0;">
      <div style="padding: 1rem; background: rgba(79,156,249,0.06); border-radius: 8px; border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-cyan);">
        <p style="font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent-cyan); margin: 0 0 0.4rem;"
          data-i18n-en="Statistical part: 1/√M"
          data-i18n-zh="统计部分：1/√M">Statistical part: 1/√M</p>
        <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; margin: 0;"
          data-i18n-en="Collect more snapshot pairs M → error decreases as 1/√M. Double M → error drops ~30%."
          data-i18n-zh="收集更多快照对 M → 误差按 1/√M 下降。M 加倍 → 误差降低约 30%。">
          Collect more snapshot pairs M → error decreases as 1/√M. Double M → error drops ~30%.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div style="padding: 1rem; background: rgba(245,158,11,0.06); border-radius: 8px; border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-amber);">
        <p style="font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent-amber); margin: 0 0 0.4rem;"
          data-i18n-en="Discretization floor: (Δt)^α"
          data-i18n-zh="离散化下限：(Δt)^α">Discretization floor: (Δt)^α</p>
        <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; margin: 0;"
          data-i18n-en="Set by the quadrature rule. α=1 (Riemann): floor ∝ Δt. α=2 (Trapezoidal): floor ∝ (Δt)². Once you hit this floor, more snapshots don't help — use finer time steps instead."
          data-i18n-zh="由积分法则决定。α=1（黎曼）：下限 ∝ Δt。α=2（梯形）：下限 ∝ (Δt)²。一旦触及此下限，更多快照无济于事——改用更细的时间步。">
          Set by the quadrature rule. α=1 (Riemann): floor ∝ Δt. α=2 (Trapezoidal): floor ∝ (Δt)². Once you hit this floor, more snapshots don't help.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="math-block" style="border-left-color: var(--accent-green);">
      <Math tex={String.raw`|\widehat{\theta}_{M,\Delta t} - \theta_*| \;\le\; C\!\left(\underbrace{(\Delta t)^\alpha}_{\text{discretization}} + \underbrace{\frac{1}{\sqrt{M}}}_{\text{statistical}}\right)`} />
    </div>

    <!-- Figure 2: M-scaling — immediately after the claim it supports -->
    <div class="paper-figure" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
      <p class="prediction-label" style="font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--accent-cyan);font-style:italic;margin-bottom:0.5rem;padding:0.5rem 0.75rem;background:rgba(79,156,249,0.06);border-radius:6px;border-left:3px solid var(--accent-cyan);"
        data-i18n-en="This figure verifies Q1: error ∝ 1/√M (statistical) then hits the discretization floor."
        data-i18n-zh="此图验证问题 1：误差 ∝ 1/√M（统计），然后触及离散化下限。">
        This figure verifies Q1: error ∝ 1/√M then hits the discretization floor.
      </p>
      <h4 style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--accent-cyan); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"
        data-i18n-en="Figure 2: M-scaling — Riemann vs Trapezoidal"
        data-i18n-zh="图 2：M-标度 — 黎曼和 vs 梯形法则">Figure 2: M-scaling — Riemann vs Trapezoidal</h4>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/figures/m_scaling_zerogap_multi_dt.png`} alt="M-scaling convergence rates" style="width: 100%; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);" loading="lazy" />
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
        <div style="padding: 0.75rem; background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.06); border-radius: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #ef4444;">
          <p style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #ef4444; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;"
            data-i18n-en="Left: Riemann (α=1) — floor at O(Δt)"
            data-i18n-zh="左：黎曼（α=1）——下限为 O(Δt)">Left: Riemann (α=1) — floor at O(Δt)</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0;"
            data-i18n-en="Error drops as 1/√M, then saturates. More data doesn't help past this floor."
            data-i18n-zh="误差按 1/√M 下降，然后饱和。超出此下限后增加数据无效。">
            Error drops as 1/√M, then saturates.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 0.75rem; background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.06); border-radius: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #22c55e;">
          <p style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #22c55e; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;"
            data-i18n-en="Right: Trapezoidal (α=2) — floor at O((Δt)²)"
            data-i18n-zh="右：梯形（α=2）——下限为 O((Δt)²)">Right: Trapezoidal (α=2) — floor at O((Δt)²)</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0;"
            data-i18n-en="Same statistical rate, but the floor is quadratically lower — why we use the trapezoidal rule."
            data-i18n-zh="相同的统计速率，但下限低了二次方——这正是我们使用梯形法则的原因。">
            Floor is quadratically lower — why we prefer the trapezoidal rule.
          </p>
        </div>
