      data-i18n-en="Question 2: What happens when snapshot pairs are far apart in time?"
      data-i18n-zh="问题 2：当快照对在时间上相距很远时会怎样？">Question 2: What happens when snapshot pairs are far apart in time?</h3>

    <p data-i18n-en="The discretization bias becomes intrinsic. When the observation gap Δt equals the fine simulation step δt (zero gap), refining the quadrature gives no extra benefit — the bias is built into the discrete model itself."
       data-i18n-zh="离散化偏差变得内在。当观测间隔 Δt 等于精细模拟步长 δt（零间隙）时，细化积分不会带来额外好处——偏差内建于离散模型本身。">
      The discretization bias becomes intrinsic. When Δt = δt (zero gap), refining quadrature gives no extra benefit.
    </p>

    <!-- Figure 3: Discrete-Model Bias — immediately after Q2 -->
