      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/figures/m_scaling_discrete_bias.png`} alt="Discrete model bias" style="width: 70%; display: block; margin: 0 auto; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="callout callout-insight" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.85rem;"
          data-i18n-en="To push accuracy below O(Δt): use finer simulation (δt &lt; Δt) and a higher-order quadrature rule. More snapshot pairs alone cannot overcome this floor."
          data-i18n-zh="要将精度推到 O(Δt) 以下：使用更精细的模拟（δt &lt; Δt）和更高阶的积分法则。仅靠增加快照对无法克服此下限。">
          To push accuracy below O(Δt): use finer simulation (δt &lt; Δt) and a higher-order quadrature rule.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

