    <h3 style="margin-top: 2.5rem; color: var(--accent-cyan);"
      data-i18n-en="Question 3: Is the least-squares solve numerically stable?"
      data-i18n-zh="问题 3：最小二乘求解在数值上稳定吗？">Question 3: Is the least-squares solve numerically stable?</h3>

