              data-i18n-zh="高斯 s=(0.5, 1.5)——交互范围因轴而异。&nabla;&Phi; 误差 12.3%，因粒子对耦合更难。">
              Gaussian with s=(0.5, 1.5) — interaction range differs by axis. &nabla;&Phi; error 12.3%, harder due to pairwise coupling.
            </p>
