        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Figure 6: Boundary Recovery -->
      <div class="paper-figure">
        <h4 style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--accent-cyan); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"
          data-i18n-en="Figure 6: Boundary Recovery — Four Stress Tests"
          data-i18n-zh="图 6：边界恢复 — 四个压力测试">Figure 6: Boundary Recovery — Four Stress Tests</h4>
        <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem;"
          data-i18n-en="How well can we recover the interaction force Φ'(r) across different models? Each panel compares the true Φ' (black dashed) with LSE (green) and NN (blue) estimators. The gray shading shows the exploration measure ρ_Φ — where particles actually visit. Estimation quality degrades sharply outside the explored region."
          data-i18n-zh="我们能多好地恢复交互力 &Phi;'(r)？每个面板对比真实 &Phi;'（黑色虚线）与 LSE（绿色）和 NN（蓝色）估计器。灰色阴影显示探索测度 &rho;<sub>&Phi;</sub>——粒子实际访问的区域。估计质量在探索区域外急剧退化。">
          How well can we recover the interaction force &Phi;'(r) across different models? Each panel compares the true &Phi;' (black dashed) with LSE (green) and NN (blue) estimators. The gray shading shows the exploration measure &rho;<sub>&Phi;</sub> — where particles actually visit. Estimation quality degrades sharply outside the explored region.
        </p>
        <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/figures/boundary_recovery.png`} alt="Boundary recovery for four stress test models" style="width: 100%; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="callout callout-insight" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.85rem;"
            data-i18n-en="Key insight: in these experiments, the gray exploration measure ρ_Φ is the dominant practical limitation. Both LSE and NN can only recover Φ' where data concentrates. Model C (Lennard-Jones) is the most extreme case: the r⁻¹² singularity keeps particles apart, leaving the short-range force poorly resolved."
            data-i18n-zh="关键洞察：在这些实验里，灰色探索测度 &rho;<sub>&Phi;</sub> 是主要的实际限制。LSE 和 NN 都只能在数据集中的区域恢复 &Phi;'。模型 C（Lennard-Jones）最为极端：r<sup>&minus;12</sup> 奇异性把粒子推开，使短程力难以解析。">
            Key insight: in these experiments, the gray exploration measure &rho;<sub>&Phi;</sub> is the dominant practical limitation. Both LSE and NN can only recover &Phi;' where data concentrates. Model C (Lennard-Jones) is the most extreme case: the r<sup>&minus;12</sup> singularity keeps particles apart, leaving the short-range force poorly resolved.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

