        <h4 style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--accent-cyan); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"
          data-i18n-en="Figure 7: All Methods Comparison"
          data-i18n-zh="图 7：所有方法对比">Figure 7: All Methods Comparison</h4>
        <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem;"
          data-i18n-en="The full picture: Self-Test (LSE and NN) vs Labeled MLE vs Sinkhorn MLE vs RBF basis, across all four stress-test models. Each row is one model; left column shows V', right column shows Φ'."
          data-i18n-zh="全景对比：自测（LSE 和 NN）vs 标签 MLE vs Sinkhorn MLE vs RBF 基函数，跨所有四个压力测试模型。每行一个模型；左列 V'，右列 &Phi;'。">
          The full picture: Self-Test (LSE and NN) vs Labeled MLE vs Sinkhorn MLE vs RBF basis, across all four stress-test models. Each row is one model; left column shows V', right column shows &Phi;'.
        </p>
        <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/figures/all_methods_combined.png`} alt="All methods comparison for four models" style="width: 100%; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);" loading="lazy" />
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
          <div style="padding: 0.75rem; background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.06); border-radius: 8px;">
            <p style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #22c55e; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;"
              data-i18n-en="Self-Test (green/blue)"
              data-i18n-zh="自测（绿色/蓝色）">Self-Test (green/blue)</p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0;"
              data-i18n-en="Tracks the target reasonably well in the tested models. NN is especially strong on V' because it does not rely on a hand-specified basis."
              data-i18n-zh="在这些测试模型中，自测通常都能较好跟踪目标势。NN 在 V' 上尤其突出，因为它不依赖手工指定的基函数。">
              Tracks the target reasonably well in the tested models. NN is especially strong on V' because it does not rely on a hand-specified basis.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div style="padding: 0.75rem; background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.06); border-radius: 8px;">
            <p style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #ef4444; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;"
              data-i18n-en="RBF basis (orange)"
              data-i18n-zh="RBF 基函数（橙色）">RBF basis (orange)</p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0;"
              data-i18n-en="Produces oscillatory estimators — the wrong basis choice amplifies noise into spurious wiggles. This confirms why basis specification matters."
              data-i18n-zh="产生振荡估计器——错误的基函数选择将噪声放大为虚假波动。这确认了基函数选择的重要性。">
              Produces oscillatory estimators — the wrong basis choice amplifies noise into spurious wiggles. This confirms why basis specification matters.
            </p>
